## 如何玩游戏
1. 请确保您有EOS账号。如果没有，推荐点击[这里](https://funeos.co)创建。

2. 请确保您已经安装了Scatter插件。如果还没有，推荐点击[这里](https://funeos.co/wiki/20)了解如何安装。

3. 在Scatter中授权游戏登录

4. 输入参与次数，点击参与，付款参与游戏

5. 游戏结束
   5.1 如果参与次数满额，点击“开启宝箱”，开始抽奖。抽出编号参与者获胜，会得到宝箱中的全部EOS

   5.2 如果参与次数未满额，点击“开启宝箱”，最后一个参与者将获得宝箱中的全部EOS

在游戏过程中，如果RAM不够，推荐点击[这里](https://funeos.co/buy-ram)购买；如果CPU或Net不够，推荐点击[这里](https://funeos.co/lease)租赁。

遇到任何问题，可以通过 QQ: 894078817 联系我们的客服，我们将很乐意为您提供服务。


## How to Play Game
1. Make sure you have an EOS account. If not, refer to [Here](https://funeos.co) to create one

2. Make sure you have install Scatter. If not, refer to [Here](https://funeos.co/wiki/20) for a tutorial

3. Authorize game in Scatter

4. Input times, click "Join" button

5. End Game
   5.1 If times are full, click "Open" to draw. The drawed number will win and obtail the all EOS in the treasure box

   5.2 If times are not full, click "Open" button, the last gamer will obtail the all EOS in the treasure box.

In game, if your RAM is not enough, refer to [Here](https://funeos.co/buy-ram) to buy some; if your CPU or NET are not enough, refer to [Here](https://funeos.co/lease) to lease some

Any problems, you can contact us by QQ: 894078817. We will be happy to serve you
